            <commentid>12175</commentid>
            <who name="Sebastian Werner">info</who>
            <bug_when>2009-09-10 14:45:20 +0200</bug_when>
            <thetext>To match other json files and to correctly allow editing in Aptana it would be nice to rename the API files which are generated by qooxdoo&#39;s build system. So instead qx.core.Object.js a file might be named qx.core.Object.json.

This should be quite easily todo and should not have side effects for most users.</thetext>
